column4: COMMENTS:  The Albuquerque Area implemented a restructured Purchased Referred Care medical priorities to better meet the needs of the service population and the mission of the organization. The Medical Priorities for the Albuquerque Area are now Priority 1 = Core, Priority 2 = Intermediate and Priority 3 = Elective.
